{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":151393,"duration_api_ms":146689,"num_turns":2,"result":"## core_business_v2/ingestion Module Overview\n\nThe ingestion module is a **Spring Boot microservice** that processes network entity (host/user) ingestion events through a **Redis-stream-backed pipeline** with a **linear state machine**.\n\n---\n\n### REST Endpoints\n\n| Method | Path | Purpose |\n|--------|------|---------|\n| POST | `/api/v1/ingestion/events` | Synchronous event ingestion (60s timeout) |\n| GET | `/api/v1/ingestion/health-check` | Health probe |\n| POST | `/api/v1/entities/query` | Query failed entities with pagination |\n| GET | `/api/v1/entities/{id}` | Get entity by ID |\n| GET | `/api/v1/entities/{id}/display-status` | Get entity processing status |\n| POST | `/api/v1/fingerprint/calculate` | Calculate attribute fingerprint |\n| POST | `/api/v1/policy/apply-existing-entities` | Mark all entities for policy reprocessing |\n\n---\n\n### Request Processing Flow\n\n```\nREST Client / External System\n        вҶ“\n  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\n  в”Ӯ  IngestionController        в”Ӯ  (or IngestionExternalConsumer for async)\n  в”Ӯ  вҶ’ publish to Redis stream  в”Ӯ\n  в”Ӯ  вҶ’ register callback future в”Ӯ\n  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n            вҶ“\n  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\n  в”Ӯ  IngestionInternalConsumer  в”Ӯ  (Redis stream consumer group)\n  в”Ӯ  вҶ’ deserialize request      в”Ӯ\n  в”Ӯ  вҶ’ call orchestrator        в”Ӯ\n  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n            вҶ“\n  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\n  в”Ӯ  IngestionOrchestrator      в”Ӯ  (routing logic)\n  в”Ӯ  1. Redis cache lookup      в”Ӯ\n  в”Ӯ  2. Creation lock acquire   в”Ӯ\n  в”Ӯ  3. DB lookup               в”Ӯ\n  в”Ӯ  4. Route to handler        в”Ӯ\n  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n            вҶ“\n  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\n  в”Ӯ  FingerprintHandler         в”Ӯ  (Strategy pattern, 4 variants)\n  в”Ӯ  Compare fingerprint + lock в”Ӯ\n  в”Ӯ  вҶ’ same attrs + lock:   noopв”Ӯ\n  в”Ӯ  вҶ’ same attrs + no lock: pollв”Ӯ\n  в”Ӯ  вҶ’ diff attrs + lock:  resetв”Ӯ\n  в”Ӯ  вҶ’ diff attrs + no lock: interrupt & retryв”Ӯ\n  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n            вҶ“\n  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\n  в”Ӯ  EntityStateMachine         в”Ӯ  (linear 4-stage pipeline)\n  в”Ӯ  PENDING вҶ’ LABELED          в”Ӯ  (LabelService)\n  в”Ӯ  LABELED вҶ’ EVALUATED        в”Ӯ  (PolicyService)\n  в”Ӯ  EVALUATED вҶ’ ENFORCED       в”Ӯ  (EnforcementService)\n  в”Ӯ  Each stage: 3 retries      в”Ӯ\n  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n            вҶ“\n  Callback completes вҶ’ HTTP response\n```\n\n---\n\n### Key Classes by Layer\n\n**Controllers** вҖ” REST entry points:\n- `IngestionController` вҖ” main ingest endpoint, publishes to Redis stream and waits on a `CompletableFuture` callback\n- `EntityController` вҖ” entity query/status inspection\n- `PolicyController` вҖ” triggers bulk reprocessing\n\n**Consumers** вҖ” Redis stream listeners:\n- `IngestionExternalConsumer` вҖ” receives from external stream, validates, forwards to internal stream\n- `IngestionInternalConsumer` вҖ” core consumer, invokes the orchestrator, completes callbacks\n\n**Orchestrator** вҖ” routing decision:\n- `IngestionOrchestrator` вҖ” determines if entity is new/cached/in-DB, acquires creation locks, delegates to the right handler\n\n**Handlers** (Strategy pattern via `FingerprintHandler` interface):\n- `NewEntityHandler` вҖ” creates entity, runs state machine\n- `CachedExistingEntityHandler` / `DbExistingEntityHandler` вҖ” computes fingerprint diff, selects one of 4 fingerprint handlers\n- `DeviceTypeChangedHandler` вҖ” handles entity type mutation (e.g., HOST вҶ’ USER_HOST_BINDING)\n- `SameAttributesWithLock/NoLockHandler`, `DifferentAttributesWithLock/NoLockHandler` вҖ” the 4 fingerprint-case handlers\n\n**State Machine**:\n- `EntityStateMachine` вҖ” runs the `PENDING вҶ’ LABELED вҶ’ EVALUATED вҶ’ ENFORCED` loop with per-stage retry (max 3), fail-point support, and interrupt checking\n- `EntityStageTransactionRunner` вҖ” wraps stage transitions in DB transactions\n\n**Stage Services** (business logic per stage):\n- `LabelService` вҖ” executes labeling/rule engine (PENDING вҶ’ LABELED)\n- `PolicyService` вҖ” evaluates policy (LABELED вҶ’ EVALUATED)\n- `EnforcementService` вҖ” applies enforcement (EVALUATED вҶ’ ENFORCED)\n\n**Registries**:\n- `IngestionCallbackRegistry` вҖ” maps requestId вҶ’ `CompletableFuture` for sync REST responses\n- `FingerprintHandlerRegistry` вҖ” maps `FingerprintCase` enum вҶ’ handler instance\n- `EntityProcessingRegistry` вҖ” tracks which entities are actively processing\n\n**Recovery/Resilience**:\n- `EntityRecoveryService` вҖ” recovers stuck entities and reclaimed pending messages\n- `StuckEntityRecoveryJob` вҖ” scheduled scan for stuck entities\n- `RedisDelayQueueUtil` / `DelayQueuePoller` вҖ” exponential backoff retry queue (2^n seconds)\n\n---\n\n### Key Design Patterns\n\n1. **Dual-stream architecture**: External stream (untrusted input) вҶ’ validation вҶ’ Internal stream (processing). This separates ingestion from execution.\n\n2. **Fingerprint-based deduplication**: Each request's attributes are hashed. If the fingerprint matches the existing entity and a lock is held, processing is skipped entirely (fast path).\n\n3. **Distributed locking**: Two Redis locks per entity вҖ” a **creation lock** (prevent duplicate inserts) and a **process lock** (ensure only one state machine instance runs at a time). Both have 30s TTL.\n\n4. **Interrupt-and-retry**: When a newer request arrives while a state machine is running, it sets an `interrupted` flag, waits for the lock, then restarts from PENDING with updated attributes.\n\n5. **Version ordering**: Redis stream message IDs serve as version numbers вҖ” stale requests (lower version than last processed) are discarded.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"fc30f8ee-cdfb-429a-9e7e-382302c29e14","total_cost_usd":0.5262693500000001,"usage":{"input_tokens":4,"cache_creation_input_tokens":21197,"cache_read_input_tokens":37223,"output_tokens":1976,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":21197,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6[1m]":{"inputTokens":4,"outputTokens":1976,"cacheReadInputTokens":37223,"cacheCreationInputTokens":21197,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.20051275,"contextWindow":1000000,"maxOutputTokens":64000},"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":92,"outputTokens":10001,"cacheReadInputTokens":1347671,"cacheCreationInputTokens":112714,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.32575660000000006,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"a5643d4d-e770-4c68-8374-ccd0031173ce"}
